Welcome to the 2024 Pleasanton games Solo Schedules Click the links below to see your solo times. You can either click on the day or click on the Grade. Good Luck to everyone! Friday Aug 30th Pibroch (Grade 4 to Open) Grade 5 piping Saturday Aug 31st solo piping (G5, G4 and G1) Grade 4 piping Sunday Sept 1st solo piping (G3 and G2) Grade 3 piping Saturday and Sunday Drumming (Snare, Tenor and Bass) Grade 2 piping Saturday Drum Majors Grade 1 piping Open piping

the 2024 Pleasanton Band Schedule https://wuspba.org/wp-content/uploads/JMM-Final-Pleasanton-Band-Schedule-2024_v2.xlsx There is a change at this years Grade 2 competition, there will be a total of 8 judges, 4 piping, 2 ensemble and 2 drumming
